  m_text: "Student bar crawls are key to Finnish student culture, and you are no
    stranger to them. Stumbling to your feet, you announce that going to one more
    place cannot hurt. It might be well past midnight already, and you have an exam
    at 8:00, but it\u2019s just getting good! Wasted as you might be, you make your
    way to the last bar, where you are stopped by the bouncer. He asks for your ID\u2026
    This can\u2019t end well."
